            "text_XeFXQe": {
              "type": "text",
              "name": "t:names.text",
              "settings": {
                "text": "<p>We don’t process exchanges for perishable items. If there’s an issue with your order quality or accuracy, contact us and we’ll resolve it with a replacement, discount, or store credit.</p><p>Where to Send Approved Returns (if requested)If our team specifically authorizes a return (rare), we’ll provide a return shipping label and instructions. Please do not send items back without approval.</p><p>European Union – 14-Day Right of WithdrawalIf your order is shipped into the EU, you may have a right to cancel or return your order within 14 days of delivery except for items that are perishable or sealed food products that are not suitable for return once unsealed (these are excluded under the withdrawal rules). For eligible items, products must be unused, in original packaging, and accompanied by proof of purchase. To initiate, email<a href=\"mailto:john@jayvending.com?subject=Product%20Return%20Inquiry&body=&cc=&bcc=\" target=\"_blank\">john@jayvending.com</a></p>",
